column5: For the first time in two years we had a server failure..or more accurately the server went down due to a total power failure at our hosts location. It all seems to be fine now, but running a bit slow as all the servers come back online and the load sharing starts to kick in. Hopefully you used the time wisely...raked the leaves or talked to your spouse or sumthin.
Welcome back everyone. What a relief.
I think I did some actual work at my workplace for a change! lol
LOL.. there goes the recession.. people actually worked for a morning....  OK.. so now what do I do with all this crap in my pants... lol
Wooohhoooo , lunch at the office sucks without OFC
HA!... thought I'd gotten the boot... was just wondering which post done it!
Power failure is better than server hardware failure...

Thanks those in charge for getting us back up! I found myself sitting in a corner of my office, huddled into a ball, rocking back and forth mumbling fish porn, fish porn under my breath! I can now begin my regularly scheduled programming! HH
Damn...I finished all my work in 3 hours this morning...now what am I supposed to do?
HAHA same to me cliff... Came crawling in this morning looking to scope posts all day... and then nothing!  Wishin I was Fishn...
Was wondering what had happened.... got working on the my trophy rack.... needed some sanding.... Sure I'm glad it's back now
WILSON!!!!  Thank the man upstairs..  I was beginning to go stir crazy..  HD
Thank God!  I can stop shaking now. Starting to suffer withdrawal. On this day, of all days, I need the distraction.
Thankfully,I had work to do today.LOL
I didn't understand.. I made my coffee, breakfast... sat down before work and didn't see OFC. I almost called in sick.

Jeez guys. Ya need to get real jobs (Except you, of course, GCD. We know yer unemployed fer chronological reasons.) For my own part I wuz way too occupied with getting my new real estate office up and running to fritter away the day talking to a bunch of fish-obsessed layabouts. I feel good about that - and really really lucky cuz it didn't happen on almost any other day of the year when I woulda been jonesing for a fix (of the OFC variety).  Just don't let it happen again. I hate when my wife sees me whispering sweet nothings to my baitcaster - for want of a better way to pass time.  JF
Do you have a hut for sale?LOL  Good luck John.
I was wondering what happened, I was wakeing up and went on to OFC and i got nothing. Went to school came home and the site was fixed.  Glad the problem was resolved
will there be an OFC baby boom in 9 months?
Meanwhile..on the 401
